		<title>地震海啸致1400人死 印尼灾区又火山喷发</title>
		<link>http://www.epochtimes.com/gb/18/10/3/n10758655.htm</link>
		<pubDate>Wed, 03 Oct 2018 16:10:46 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[国际要闻]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[新闻]]></category>
