		<title>美国不再向外交人员的同性伴侣发放签证</title>
		<link>http://www.epochtimes.com/gb/18/10/2/n10756972.htm</link>
		<pubDate>Wed, 03 Oct 2018 00:28:21 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[北美新闻]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[国际要闻]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[新闻]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[美国移民]]></category>
