		<title>强台风潭美袭日酿灾 交通混乱45万户停电</title>
		<link>http://www.epochtimes.com/gb/18/10/1/n10753512.htm</link>
		<pubDate>Mon, 01 Oct 2018 10:44:23 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[国际要闻]]></category>
